msgid ""
"To enable this feature and select a self-ordering type, access the :ref:`POS "
"settings <pos/use/settings>`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Mobile self-"
"order & Kiosk` section, and select a :guilabel:`Self Ordering` type under "
