"DPO Pay payment terminals do not require an :doc:`IoT system </applications/"
"general/iot>` to operate."
msgstr ""
"DPO Pay決済端末は、動作に\\ :doc:`IoTシステム </applications/general/iot>`\\ "
"を必要としません。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/dpo.rst:16
