"フィールドが `2` 以上に設定されている場合）。この価格は、:guilabel:`コンボの"
"選択`\\ で定義された最も安価なプロダクトの価格に基づいて自動的に計算されます"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:88
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Extra Price` field is used to set an additional charge for a "
"specific product in the combo choice, e.g., to cover higher costs or "
"encourage upselling. This extra price is applied each time a customer "
"selects that product within the combo choice."
msgstr ""
