#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/manage.rst:85
msgid "Lazada package statuses"
msgstr "Lazada\\ の梱包ステータス"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/manage.rst:87
msgid ""
"Understanding Lazada package statuses is crucial for effective order "
"management:"
msgstr "Lazada\\ の梱包ステータスを理解することは、効果的なオーダ管理に不可欠です："

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/manage.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Package Pending on Lazada`: The package is awaiting receipt, "
"tagging, or processing in the warehouse system."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Package Pending on Lazada`：梱包は、倉庫システムでの受領、タグ付け"
"、または処理を待機しています。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/manage.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Package Confirmed on Lazada`: The package has been packed by the "
"seller or warehouse and is confirmed ready for courier pickup or dropoff. "
"Lazada is notified and updates the order status."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Package Confirmed on Lazada`：梱包は販売者または倉庫によって梱包さ"
"れ、配送業者による受取または持込の準備が完了していることが確定されました。"
"Lazada\\ に通知され、オーダステータスが更新されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/manage.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Ready to Ship on Lazada`: The order is ready for shipment. Lazada "
"is notified and updates the order status."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ready to Ship on Lazada`：オーダは出荷準備が完了しています。"
"Lazada\\ に通知され、オーダステータスが更新されます。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/manage.rst:96
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivered on Lazada`: The parcel has been dropped off or picked "
